<title>SRI LANKA: Sri Lanka Glass posts lower net in Q1.</title>
<headline>Sri Lanka Glass posts lower net in Q1.</headline>
<dateline>COLOMBO 1996-08-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Unaudited results of Ceylon Glass Company for the first quarter of the 1996/1997 financial year.</p>
<p>(in millions of rupees unless stated):</p>
<p>			   Q1 1996/97	    Q1 1995/96</p>
<p>    Turnover	     129.68    vs	 154.23</p>
<p>    Net profit	    14.18    vs	  15.66</p>
<p>    Tax			---		     ---</p>
<p>NOTE - Results are for the three months to June 30, 1996. Ceylon Glass Company is Sri Lanka's monopoly glass bottle manufacturer. Company profits are not taxed due to cumulative losses in the two previous financial years, a company spokesman said.</p>
<p>--Colombo newsroom tel 941-434319</p>
